		{
			"type": "paragraph",
			"children": [
				{
					"type": "text",
					"text": "Attention!",
					"bold": true
				},
				{
					"type": "text",
					"text": "If possible, wear a T-shirt while snorkeling instead of using sunscreen. Sunscreen can easily get into the water, and the substances in it can inhibit coral growth, gradually damaging them. The high level of tourism in these areas poses a significant threat to the future of coral reefs."
				}
			]
